    Class Description
    AndQuery
    Query testing if all its sub-queries are satisfied.
    CoreQueries
    This class is a convenience class of static methods that brings together queries of all types.
    CountQuery
    Checks that an integer ('count') is within a range.
    EdgeListNodes
    A Query to select start, end, other-end or both-ends Nodes of a list of Edges
    EdgeNodes
    A Query to select start, end, other-end or both-ends Nodes of an Edge
    EdgeNodeSelection
    An enum to describe the tips of an Edge.
    ElementLabel
    A Query for Specialized objects which have a class identifier, classId, also called label.
    ElementName
    A Query for Identity objects, which have a unique identifier id, also called a name.
    ElementProperty
    A Query to check that an object has a property and (optionally) a value.
    FilteredList<T>
    A list filtered by a Query.
    IsClass
    Checks if an object is of a given class within a list of classes.
    IsQuery
    Checks that an object is a Query.
    IsStringList  
    Multiplicity
    The four main multiplicities used in UML.
    NodeEdges
    A Query to select Edges linked to a Node.
    NodeListEdges
    A Query to select In, OUT or all edges of a list of Nodes.
    NotQuery
    Query testing if all its sub-queries are not satisfied.
    OrQuery
    Query testing if at least one its sub-queries is satisfied.
    QGraphException
    A class for Exceptions arising in the qgraph library.
    Queryable
    The ancestor class for the Query system.
    QueryAdaptor
    An ancestor implementation for queries with default behaviour for all methods of Queryable but submit(...).
    QueryList
    An ancestor for compound queries grouping multiple queries.
    SelectQuery
    A query to select items based on multiplicities.
    SequenceQuery
    Chains a sequence of queries, i.e. the result() of each query serves as an input into submit(...) of the next query.
    SizeQuery
    Query testing if the size of a Sizeable object is within a specified range.
    StartsWith
    A query to check that a String starts with a given sequence of characters.
    TextTranslations  
    TreeQuery
    Get parts of a Tree starting from a TreeNode.
    XorQuery
    Query testing if exactly one its sub-queries is satisfied.
